data.description: This amazing 6-bed, 3-bath residence has room for everyone & everything! Energy-efficient, garage with extended driveway, and front patio are features that can't be left unsaid. The interior boasts a great room with a soft palette & stone-look tile flooring through main traffic areas. Convenient bonus room on the ground level is ideal for an office or an extra bedroom. The kitchen showcases ample wood cabinetry, lots of counter space, SS appliances, and a peninsula with a breakfast bar. Upstairs, you'll find a spacious loft with vaulted ceilings & plush carpet perfect for a TV room. The primary bedroom has a full bathroom with a dual sink & a walk-in closet. The large backyard offers a covered patio & lots of potential for entertaining. New AC and New Roof installed in 2022.
